OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1777209066
OL,3,CRapist caught by DNA more than 20
OL,4,Cyears after raping Bradford schoolgirl
OL,6,FA rapist who preyed on a schoolgirl
OL,7,Fhas been jailed 22 years later after
OL,8,Fhe was finally caught by DNA.
OL,10,FAbdul Qayum assaulted the 14-year-old
OL,11,Fat a flat in Bradford in June 2004,
OL,12,Fwhen he spotted her while a passenger
OL,13,Fin a friend's car.
OL,15,FA court heard he had ordered her into
OL,16,Fthe car, before taking her back to the
OL,17,Fflat and plying her with cannabis and
OL,18,Falcohol.
OL,20,FAfter she became unwell, he put her to
OL,21,Fbed before later raping her.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1777209066
OL,3,CRapist caught by DNA more than 20
OL,4,Cyears after raping Bradford schoolgirl
OL,6,FThe girl, now a woman in her thirties,
OL,7,Fwas able to call the police and escape
OL,8,Fthe flat and Qayum was later arrested,
OL,9,Fbut let go after it was ultimately
OL,10,Fdecided there would not be enough
OL,11,Fevidence to prosecute him.
OL,13,FQayum was re-arrested in 2023 after
OL,14,Fmale DNA on swabs taken from the
OL,15,Fvictim proved a hit.
OL,17,FHe was jailed for 14 years at Bradford
OL,18,FCrown Court on Friday and placed on
OL,19,Fthe Sex Offenders Register for life.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
