FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1777209066
OL,3,CRapist caught by DNA more than 20
OL,4,Cyears after raping Bradford schoolgirl
OL,6,FDirectly addressing her rapist, the
OL,7,Fwoman said in a victim impact
OL,8,Fstatement read in court how he "had no
OL,9,Fright to take me away from living a
OL,10,Fnormal happy life".
OL,12,FAdmitting she "blamed herself" at the
OL,13,Ftime, the victim said: "I feel as
OL,14,Fthough I am the one who has been
OL,15,Fserving a sentence from the damage you
OL,16,Fcaused.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1777209066
OL,3,CRapist caught by DNA more than 20
OL,4,Cyears after raping Bradford schoolgirl
OL,6,F"What you did will never leave me, but
OL,7,FI can finally move on after some
OL,8,Fclosure and start to heal the best I
OL,9,Fcan after it has consumed me for so
OL,10,Flong."
OL,12,FThe investigation into Qayum came
OL,13,Fabout as part of a major review by
OL,14,FWest Yorkshire Police into non-recent
OL,15,Fsexual crimes, using advanced DNA
OL,16,Ftechnology.
OL,18,FDespite giving no comment in police
OL,19,Finterviews and pleading not guilty, he
OL,20,Fwas found guilty by a jury.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@FO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
