FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1777209066
OL,3,CRapist caught by DNA more than 20
OL,4,Cyears after raping Bradford schoolgirl
OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Richard Ord, of the
OL,7,FMajor Investigation Review Team, said:
OL,8,F"Qayum preyed on the victim, who was a
OL,9,Fvulnerable young schoolgirl, in the
OL,10,Fworst of circumstances, and she has
OL,11,Fhad to live with the impact of his
OL,12,Factions for all these years.
OL,26,@pD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1777209066
OL,3,CRapist caught by DNA more than 20
OL,4,Cyears after raping Bradford schoolgirl
OL,6,F"He denied the offence at the time,
OL,7,Fand unfortunately the evidence
OL,8,Favailable then was not sufficient to
OL,9,Fprogress to a charge. Thankfully,
OL,10,Fadvances in forensic science meant we
OL,11,Fwere able to reopen the case on the
OL,12,Fbasis of new DNA evidence and progress
OL,13,Fthe investigation to see Qayum held
OL,14,Fcriminally responsible.
OL,16,F"We hope it will provide some degree
OL,17,Fof comfort to the victim to know that
OL,18,Fhe has now finally been brought to
OL,19,Fjustice."
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU{D@IO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
